      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will likely require significant mechanical attention and cosmetic repairs to be roadworthy. The exterior has several noticeable dents and paint fading, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. It starts but runs roughly, making it a potential project car for someone with the right tools and expertise. It is priced to reflect its current state and the work needed.",
