    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this exceptional vehicle, a specimen that reflects the highest standards of automotive preservation. Maintained in showroom condition, this automobile exhibits an impeccable exterior finish paired with a pristine, smoke-free interior. Every component has been meticulously curated to ensure an uncompromising driving experience. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection in both aesthetics and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
